  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK267">
<l>cuṭaccuṭarum poṉpō loḷiviṭun tuṉpañ</l>
<l>cuṭaccuṭa nōṟkiṟ pavarkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Just as gold is purified as heated in the fire, will those shine, who have endured the burning of pain (in frequent austerities).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
